      <strong>Data Security:</strong>
      <p>Reasonable measures are taken to protect data processed by this service. However, as the service is provided “as is,” no absolute security guarantees can be made.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Data Retention:</strong>
      <p>Data is retained only for as long as necessary to train the GPT model and will be disposed of once it is no longer needed.</p>
    </li>
